text:
Bonjour beautiful people!! <!channel>

Good job to the runners today :clap: :woman-running::skin-tone-2: :hand_with_index_finger_and_thumb_crossed: 

You guys did amazing!!! The real race is the friends we made along the way!

A round of applause for <@U02UAQKR56C> who ran faster than Tom Hanks in Forrest Gump!

<@U041S3WQKND> came in at second and flexed his calves to everyone behind him!

And I finished a close 3rd place and made sure all of YouTube heard about it!! <https://youtube.com/shorts/lqKlwzyBJ4Y?feature=share|https://youtube.com/shorts/lqKlwzyBJ4Y?feature=share>

Good job everyone <@U02MANZL55F> <@U041DBXGPC4> <@U01JYRB9DL2> <@U040V1EQYMS> <@U02UAQKR56C> <@U041S3WQKND> thank you to all who came out today. 

Made with love, 
Vinay 

Ps happy birthday week- wish <@U041DBXGPC4> a happy birthday (4/20) and <@U01JYRB9DL2> (4/28)!! :birthday:

Pps May 3-4 conference up next!! 

With some assist from Cherie Lum
